OL,3,CMum of murdered son says action on
OL,4,Cknife crime not 'quick enough'
OL,6,FThe mum of a son murdered in a 'Rambo
OL,7,Fknife' style street attack says action
OL,8,Fbeing taken to tackle knife crime is
OL,9,Fnot coming "quick enough".
OL,11,FIn an interview with ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,12,FJoanne Crewe said the "catastrophic"
OL,13,Floss of her son, Lee Crewe, was a
OL,14,F"life sentence".
OL,16,FDavid Sisman, 21, stabbed Lee, 36, in
OL,17,Fthe Maindee area of Newport on May 14
OL,18,F2024, and was sentenced to 24 years in
OL,19,Fprison.
