OL,6,FDescribing the incident, Joanne said:
OL,7,F"You can see on CCTV, he (Sisman)
OL,8,Fpulls a knife, and Lee backs away. And
OL,9,Fhe just lunged at him. Lee didn't
OL,10,Fstand a chance. He intended to do
OL,11,Fserious damage with that knife."
OL,13,FDespite claiming self-defence after
OL,14,Fstabbing Crewe once in the chest,
OL,15,FSisman was found guilty of murder by a
OL,16,Fjury at Newport Crown Court.
OL,18,FNow, Joanne has turned her efforts to
OL,19,Fraising awareness.
