OL,3,CMum of murdered son says action on
OL,4,Cknife crime not 'quick enough'
OL,6,F"Everyone says more needs to be done,
OL,7,Fit's fine saying that, let's do
OL,8,Fsomething about it. We need to be more
OL,9,Fproactive in the law, in educating
OL,10,Fyoungsters that it's not good to carry
OL,11,Fa knife."
OL,13,F"I can't stress enough, it's
OL,14,Fsenseless, it's pointless, why carry a
OL,15,Fknife? Because it's going to ruin so
OL,16,Fmany people's lives.
OL,18,F"Life doesn't seem to mean much to
OL,19,Fthese people carrying knives. The
OL,20,Fdamage they do is catastrophic.
