OL,6,F"It's heartbreaking to see other
OL,7,Ffamilies in the same boat as me. And
OL,8,Fit is a promise, we together,
OL,9,Fcollectively I feel, get there in the
OL,10,Fend, but it's not coming quick enough.
OL,11,FIt needs to stop now."
OL,13,FJoanne added: "He (Sisman) can come
OL,14,Fout after 24 years, my son will never
OL,15,Fcome back. We've got the life
OL,16,Fsentence."
OL,18,FIt comes as police forces across Wales
OL,19,Ftake part in Operation Sceptre - a
OL,20,Fnational amnesty to reduce knife-
OL,21,Frelated crime.
