OL,6,FSceptre will see officers carrying out
OL,7,Fseven days of anti-knife crime work,
OL,8,Fand education in school, to highlight
OL,9,Fit's impact.
OL,11,FKnife amnesty bins will also be open
OL,12,Fat five stations across Gwent for
OL,13,Fpeople to deposit dangerous knives and
OL,14,Fblades safely and securely.
