OL,6,FSergeant Phill Jones, who is leading
OL,7,FGwent's Sceptre operation, said:
OL,8,F"Knife crime can have a devastating
OL,9,Fimpact on our communities and while
OL,10,Fpolicing plays a big role in reducing
OL,11,Fknife crime, we cannot address the
OL,12,Fissue alone.
OL,14,F"As a service, we continue to speak
OL,15,Fwith young people, in particular, to
OL,16,Feducate them on the consequences of
OL,17,Fcarrying bladed articles.
