OL,6,F"Carrying a knife doesn't protect you
OL,7,F` it can make a situation worse ` so
OL,8,Fif you know someone who is carrying a
OL,9,Fknife in your area, please report it
OL,10,Fto us immediately.
OL,12,F"By providing us with that
OL,13,Finformation, you could be saving the
OL,14,Flife of someone you love."
